<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Lazio of Rome 1, Man. United 0 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	MONTE CARLO, Monaco (AP) -- Marcelo Salas scored in the 35th  
minute Friday night, leading Lazio of Rome over Manchester United 
in the European SuperCup. 
</P>
<P>
	Salas scored on a pass from Roberto Mancini, beating goalkeeper  
Raimond Van der Gouw. 
</P>
<P>
	Manchester United won the European Champions Cup last season and  
Lazio won the final Cup Winners Cup. That tournament has been 
merged into the UEFA Cup this season. 
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
